    <h3 style="margin-top:30px">🍕 The Core Pizza Pack — How It Works</h3>
    <p>Before getting into SKUs, every team member needs to understand how the product physically works — the same explanation ends up in 80% of CX calls and every brief.</p>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-tile">
