        <tr><td>BPA-free silicone, microwave-safe, freezer-safe, dishwasher-safe</td><td>&quot;Medical-grade,&quot; &quot;food-safe-certified&quot; (without spec)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>&quot;Made for pizza&quot; · &quot;Soggy Slice Syndrome&quot;</td><td>&quot;Multi-purpose food container&quot;</td></tr>
