      <div class="type-spec-use">Section headings · editorial copy · emotional/featured moments</div>
      <p style="font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--pp-charcoal);margin:0">The smarter way to store leftover pizza.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="type-spec">
      <div class="type-spec-name">Inter</div>
      <div class="type-spec-use">Body copy · UI · product pages · CX templates</div>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:var(--pp-text);margin:0">Five removable, microwave-safe divider trays slot into one BPA-free silicone container that collapses and expands to fit your slices — saving roughly 70% of your fridge space versus a flat pizza box.</p>
