        <img class="creative-img" src="data:image/webp;base64," alt="Instagram Feed ad — Amazon's viral kitchen must-have, 693 reactions">
        <div class="creative-meta">Instagram Feed · Static + UGC framing</div>
        <div class="creative-caption"><strong>"Amazon's viral kitchen must-have"</strong>Native-feeling creative leaning hard on the viral / Amazon-must-have framing. <strong>693 reactions and 48 comments</strong> visible — this is the post that pulled the most engagement and is the highest social-proof asset in the current rotation. <em>Pattern hits: social proof front and center + native authentic creative + emotion over logic (FOMO / "everyone has this").</em></div>
        <div class="creative-tags"><span class="creative-tag">Viral framing</span><span class="creative-tag">UGC feel</span><span class="creative-tag">High engagement</span></div>
      </div>
