        <div class="creative-caption"><strong>"Fridge fight again? Pizza Pack stores up to 8 slices neatly. No boxes, no bags, no mess."</strong>Stories-format ad opening with a specific, relatable problem ("fridge fight again?") and resolving with a one-line product promise plus a concrete number (8 slices). <em>Pattern hits: specific relatable problem + one clear simple message + contrast/switch framing (boxes & bags vs. Pizza Pack).</em></div>
