      <p style="margin:0">Don't add new hashtags to the official set without Marketing approval. Trending tags can be added on a per-post basis but should never displace the core set above. <strong>#TikTokMadeMeBuyIt</strong> and <strong>#AsSeenOnSharkTank</strong> are our highest-discovery tags — keep them in rotation.</p>
